ak mi budeš stáť v ceste.

163
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:14,890
Ten bastard...

164
00:12:17,550 --> 00:12:19,500
Priblíž to na maximum, priblíž to!

165
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:21,640
