tak som sa na to pripravil!

187
00:13:45,290 --> 00:13:47,990
Nevidíte, že máme na sebe uniformy?

188
00:13:47,990 --> 00:13:50,350
My sme

189
00:13:50,350 --> 00:13:51,980
študenti!

190
00:13:51,980 --> 00:13:54,000
Sme študenti.

191
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:56,360
Ak ste vy dvaja študenti,

192
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:58,520
potom ja som G-Dragon.

193
00:13:58,520 --> 00:13:59,330
Čože?

194
00:13:59,330 --> 00:14:02,130
Ani slovo! A tú vec mi odovzdajte!

195
00:14:02,130 --> 00:14:04,350
Prečo?

196
00:14:04,350 --> 00:14:08,820
Na streche robíte perverzné fotky.
Dajte mi to!

197
00:14:08,860 --> 00:14:10,960
Ahjussi, zasahujete do súkromia!

198
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:13,640
Je to osobný majetok.

199
00:14:13,700 --> 00:14:15,700
Ak to nič nebude,

200
00:14:15,700 --> 00:14:18,130
